<section id="sec.intro">
  <title>Introduction</title>

  <para>This guide provides instructions for installing &sr;, its
  sample data sets, and &sr; documentation on the &pf; platform.  &sr;
  can be installed from an <!--%= doc.ifP(Doc::Linux) {%Q{-->RPM<!--}}
  %--><!--%= doc.ifP(Doc::OSX) {%Q{-->disk image (DMG)<!--}} %--> or
  from its source code.</para>

  <para>&pf; platform guidelines are listed in <xref
  linkend="tbl.pltfm_req"/>.</para>
    
<!--%= doc.ifP(Doc::Linux) { %Q{-->
   <para>Linux has been tested on the specified systems and RPMs are
   provided for these systems.  &sr; may work on other Linux systems
   as well.</para>
<!--}} %-->

  <para>
    Disk space requirements <!--%= doc.ifNotP(Doc::Irix) {%Q{-->for a source code installation<!--}} %--> are listed in
    <xref linkend="tbl.disk_space"/>.
  </para>

